line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">第四章&nbsp; 报名、填报志愿</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第十条 凡符合免试申请条件的退役大学生士兵于2022年2月16日9：00-2月24日17:00自行登录江西软件职业技术大学官网（网址：http://www.jxuspt.com/）“专升本报名入口”，按要求填写、上传个人基本信息（包括本人手机号）、专科毕业院校、报考专业、在校期间成绩、身份证照片、退伍证明照片等相关信息。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">第五章&nbsp; 综合考查评价办法</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第十一条 根据我校疫情防控相关要求，我校综合考查采取线上面试形式进行，将全程录像并保存备查，学校纪检监察部门对面试全过程进行监督。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第十二条 线上面试时间：2022年2月25日9:00-17:00。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第十三条 线上面试平台：手机钉钉APP面试。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第十四条 线上面试方案</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1、专家选聘：按专业大类分组，每组由5位专家组成，其中1名主考。教务处会同纪检人员选定并通知面试专家。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2、面试命题：面试命题采用现场出题的方式，面试专家组提前1小时现场命题。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3、考生面试：考生提前30分钟进入手机钉钉APP候考群候考签到、并按指定顺序打开视频逐一面试，面试专家随机抽选面试题目给考生回答，回答完毕等待面试专家通知关闭视频才完成面试。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4、成绩评定：面试专家根据考生答题表现当场打分，评分去掉一个最高分和一个最低分，取其平均分(保留2位小数点)作为考生的最终成绩。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第十五条 面试考察范围</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1、专业技能：主要考察报考专业职业适应性或职业技能的掌握情况，占综合成绩60%。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2、综合素质：含语言表达能力、逻辑思维能力、应变能力、职业兴趣等，占综合成绩40%。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">第六章&nbsp;录取办法</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第十六条 录取工作贯彻公开、公平、公正原则，严格按照教育厅有关文件执行：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1、严格执行梯度志愿顺序投档录取原则；</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2、学校按专业门类招生计划数依据综合评价总成绩从高分至低分的顺序择优录取，如遇综合总成绩相同时，按专业技能考察成绩排序择优录取，若专业技能考察成绩相同，则再次组织参加学校面试择优录取。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3、若招生类别专业第一志愿未录取完成，学校根据江西省教育考试院提供的第二志愿报考江西软件职业技术大学考生名单，按第一志愿录取的工作流程进行。以此类推，直至征集志愿录取结束。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4、凡符合录取条件的考生，不得要求学校退档，学校也不得以考生自愿放弃为由退档。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">第七章 &nbsp;学费和待遇</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第十七条 &nbsp;进入本科阶段学习的学生，按学校2020级规定的学费收费标准交纳有关费用。“专升本”学生享受普通本科生相同的待遇。学生学习期满，各科成绩合格，由学校颁发专科起点的本科毕业证书和学位证书。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第十八条 &nbsp;资助政策：所有专升本录取退役大学生士兵新生可享受每年3000元/人奖学金（区块链专业除外），区块链技术专业录取的退役大学生士兵可享受每年1万元/人奖学金。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第十九条 &nbsp;退学退费办法：如学生有特殊原因要求退学，我校按照江西省教育厅《江西省民办高校退学退费办法》的规定，办理退学退费手续。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">第八章 &nbsp;附则</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第二十条 &nbsp;本章程若与国家法律、法规、章程、规范和上级有关政策不符，按国家法律、法规、章程、规范和上级有关政策执行。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第二十一条 &nbsp;我校不委托任何中介机构或个人进行高考招生录取工作，请考生和家长不要上当受骗。对以学校名义进行非法招生宣传和招生录取等活动的中介机构或个人，学校保留依法追究其责任的权利。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第二十二条 &nbsp;本章程未尽事宜，由我校与各省（市、区）高考招生职能部门协商解决。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第二十三条 本章程自公布之日起生效，由我校招生办公室负责解释。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;第二十四条&nbsp;&nbsp;联系方式：</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 招生咨询电话：0791-83792888（传真）</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;学校网址：http://www.jxuspt.com/</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;举报电话：0791－83792364</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: right;">江西软件职业技术大学</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: right;">2022年2月12日</p><p><br/></p>